Class HistoryManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • editor.HistoryManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable

    public class HistoryManager
extends Object
implements Observable
    HistoryManager manages the command history by saving in stacks the memento systems created after each command altering the buffer or the selection.
    See Also:
    Undo, Redo
